---
title: Argentinian-Style Cod with Almond Herb Chimichurri
description: This dish will take you to Argentina and back with the help of two distinct elements. On the one hand, there’s chimichurri, which is a thick herb sauce that we’ve bulked up with almonds. And on the other hand, there’s salmuera. Basting the cod with this Argentinian version of brine keeps it moist and incredibly flavorful.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/whitefish-with-almond-herb-chimi-f2eeb626.jpg
